# KNN Classification 

# Objective
Implement K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) algorithm for classification.

# Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

# Results
- Best K = 5
- Achieved high accuracy on test data

# Conclusion
KNN performs well for small datasets but depends heavily on K value and scaling.
Dataset link- https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/iris
